<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="flash-v">flash <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /flæʃ/    美 /flæʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 闪光；(使) 闪耀：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Police cars arrived with their blue lights flashing.
警车到了，蓝色的警灯闪烁着。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why is that driver <strong>flashing</strong> his lights <strong>at</strong> / <strong>towards</strong> me?
那个司机为什么朝我闪车灯呢？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>闪现；突然想到：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A smile <strong>flashed across</strong> Kathy's face.
凯西的脸上闪过一丝微笑。</p><footer>2008 湖北</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Memories <strong>flashed through his mind</strong>.
回忆掠过他的脑海。</p><footer>2008 江苏</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A good idea flashed into my mind.
我突然想到一个好的主意。</p></div></div>